config = dapt.Config(path=conf_path)
create_database_entries(config)
db = dapt.db.Sheet(config=config)
expected = [{'id': 't1', 'start-time': '2019-09-06 17:23', 'end-time':
    '2019-09-06 17:36', 'status': 'finished', 'a': 2, 'b': 4, 'c': 6}, {
    'id': 't2', 'start-time': '', 'end-time': '', 'status': '', 'a': 10,
    'b': 10, 'c': ''}, {'id': 't3', 'start-time': '', 'end-time': '',
    'status': '', 'a': 10, 'b': -10, 'c': ''}]
actual = db.get_table()
assert actual == expected, 'Cannot read the Google Sheet correctly.  Nothing else should work.'
